MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1032. No. 93AP-220. State ex rel. Smith v. Provincial Am. Transport, Inc. Franklin County,

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of Provincial American Transport, Inc.’s application for dismissal of its appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective December 5, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
